{{italic title}}
The '''''Numismatic Circular''''' is an international [[periodical]] published by [[Spink (publisher)|Spink]] since 1892 based in [[London]]. Now published six times a year, the ''Circular'' offers [[coins]], books and [[banknotes]] for sale at fixed prices and features articles of [[numismatic]] interest. It is believed to be the oldest such publication in existence. <ref>[http://www.spink.com/resources/nc/numismatic_circular.asp The Spink Numismatic Circular: Coins, Books and Banknotes from Spink website]</ref>

